settings.content_text: The internal layout is designed to drastically reinforce the cable heads, which is where most cables tend to fail. With a phenomenal 25,000 in the bend test, this cable will easily outlive your device.
Far from your everyday cord, the Titan Cable delivers lightning-fast charging with its thicker internal wires, higher 2.4A amperage capabilities and highly conductive materials.
Charge your phone, speakers, camera or even your Xbox controller with our cable to keep all your devices boosted and ready to go!
The 90° design keeps the cable flat and out of the way. Perfect for watching shows or gaming with your friends!

Our Safe Disconnect feature ensures your battery stays protected from overcharging. Say goodbye to worries about damaging your device while leaving it plugged in overnight or for extended periods. With the Titan Smart Cable, your battery's health is safeguarded, ensuring longevity and optimal performance.

Keep your space organized and clutter-free with our innovative Tidy Cable Tie. No more tangled messes or unruly cords. Easily wrap and secure your cable with our convenient tie, maintaining a neat and tidy setup wherever you go.

We revolutionised cable durability.  Using the best materials, our cables outlive the rest, challenging the industry's break-and-replace cycle. Our goal? Deliver a sustainable solution that cuts e-waste for your home. Titan stands for lasting quality, unlike others who build to break. Choose Titan, choose sustainability.

Join our million-strong community who've shaped the Titan Smart Cable over five years. Your feedback has driven our growth, making us leaders in reliable, evolving charging solutions. Experience the Titan difference today.

settings.tab_content: The Fork attachment smoothly glides along your trapezius muscles, starting from the upper neck area down to your shoulders. It can also be used to massage the Achilles tendon and calf muscles. Primarily designed for targeting trigger points and addressing lower back discomfort. While it can be applied on either side of the spine, avoid direct contact with bones.

Primarily suited for larger muscle groups such as the glutes, hamstrings, and quadriceps. For stress relief and addressing pressure points, consider using it on the soles of your feet and around the upper back and neck area.
Crafted for gliding across broad muscle surfaces, this attachment is optimal for targeting dense muscle groups like the pectorals, glutes, and quadriceps.

Perfect for pinpointing localized muscle knots and tackling tension at its source. Ideal for precise muscle treatment and smaller muscle groups such as the soles of the feet, neck, and calves. Excellent for trigger point therapy but avoid prolonged use on any muscle area exceeding 15 seconds.

settings.text: Through continuous innovation and listening to our customers, we've transformed our charging cable into the pinnacle of reliability and convenience for your daily needs

settings.accordion_question: How durable is the Titan Smart Cable?
settings.accordion_answer: Our cable is engineered with durability as a top priority. Constructed with triple nylon braiding and reinforced metal connector tips, it withstands up to 1,500 lbs of force, ensuring longevity that outlasts your device. Say goodbye to frayed or worn-out cables with Titan Power.

settings.accordion_question: What devices is this cable compatible with?
settings.accordion_answer: Our charging cable will work with all conventional mobile devices, including new releases. We cannot list all the models but see a list of brands below that will support our cable. You can also use our cable to change a whole range of everyday items, such as your speakers, headphones, tablets, cameras and controllers. Please note much larger devices like MacBooks cannot be charged with this cable.

We have so much confidence in our cables durability that we offer a lifetime warranty and 60-day warranty on all other products. This means that if anything happens, we'll send you a brand new charger, free of charge! The warranty covers any defects in material or workmanship. Furthermore, if any unexpected or unreasonable damage occurs this will be covered. Any intentional damage or damage caused by unconventional use will not be covered. Please note that any cable sent out to you as a replacement will not be covered by this warranty.

settings.accordion_question: Is this cable safe to use with my device?
settings.accordion_answer: This cable delivers fast charging at an amperage level that is supported by your mobile device and will therefore not cause any damage.

settings.accordion_question: Does the Titan Smart Cable support fast charging?
settings.accordion_answer: Absolutely! Our cable is designed for ultra-fast charging, delivering quick and efficient power to your devices, saving you time and keeping you connected.

settings.accordion_question: How long is the Titan Power Cable?
settings.accordion_answer: We offer the Titan Smart Cable in three convenient lengths: 1.2m, 1.8m, and 3.0m, allowing you to choose the perfect length for your charging needs and setup.

settings.accordion_question: How does the Titan Smart Cable prevent bending and fraying?
settings.accordion_answer: Our cable features a unique 90° head design that prevents bending and strain on the cable, ensuring it remains intact and free from wear and tear even with frequent use.

settings.accordion_question: Can I use the Titan Smart Cable with other accessories like power banks or car chargers?
settings.accordion_answer: Yes, our cable is compatible with a variety of accessories, including power banks and car chargers, offering versatility and convenience for charging on the go.

settings.accordion_question: Does the Titan Smart Cable come with a cable tie for storage and organization?
settings.accordion_answer: Yes, each Titan Power Cable includes a convenient cable tie, allowing you to neatly wrap and secure the cable when not in use, keeping your space tidy and organized.

settings.multi_columns_block_copy: Experience peace of mind with our 100% satisfaction guarantee. If you're not absolutely delighted with your Titan product, let us know, and we'll make it right. Your satisfaction is our top priority.

Not sure about investing in a Titan Smart Cable? Take advantage of our 30-day return policy. If you're not completely satisfied with your purchase for any reason, simply return it within 30 days for a full refund. No hassle, no questions asked.

Rest assured, your Titan Smart Cable is backed by our lifetime warranty. In the rare event your Titan product encounters any faults or breaks through no fault of yours, we'll provide a free replacement.
